Such Roadtrip
=============

Roadtrip for Android helps you create a scrapbook of your trip automatically with photos, tweets, and other updates. Roadtrip will automatically organize all of your and your friendsâ€™ activities and plot them on a map in the context of your road trip, so that you can relive the experience again.

